  .guide
    .content
      h2 Construction
      p Idaho statute specifies the proportion and spacing for the flag’s visual elements in feet and inches.
      p The flag should have a hoist of 4 feet, 4 inches and a fly of 5 feet, 6 inches.
      p The seal should be 21 inches in diameter.
      p The banner inscribed “The State of Idaho” should be 3 inches tall by 29 inches wide, placed 8.5 inches from the bottom edge. The letters should be 2 inches tall.
